What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Ultraviolet Disinfection Equipment Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Ultraviolet Disinfection Equipment Market

Ultraviolet disinfection equipment market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 13.95% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rapid increase in the initiatives undertaken by governments and various authorities regarding the usage of the UV disinfection systems is an essential factor driving the ultraviolet disinfection equipment market.

UV (Ultraviolet) disinfection equipment is defined as the type of instruments and components that in collection make up the UV disinfection system. The collection of these equipment are used in the treatments and processing of numerous applications such as water treatment, industrial equipment cleaning, devices cleansing among others. It is a chemical-free disinfectant process which involves exposure to ultraviolet rays helping in the removal of any unwanted bacteria or infections.

Rise in the levels of concern amongst the world regarding the availability of drinkinga water is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also increase in the advancements in technologies along with the availability of UV LED based disinfecting systems, increase in the benefits of this system as it is environmental friendly while being highly effective in removal of any infective bacteria, rise in the extensive use of UV disinfection equipment in healthcare facilities for disinfecting hospital environment and rise in the demand for UV disinfection equipment to combat COVID-19 pandemic are the major factors among others boosting the ultraviolet disinfection equipment market. Moreover, rise in the demand for ultrapure water and rise in the adoption of UV disinfection equipment for water and wastewater treatment worldwide will further create new opportunities for ultraviolet disinfection equipment market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, lower cost of conventional disinfectants compared to UV lights and lack of residual ability of UV disinfection equipment are the major factors among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the ultraviolet disinfection equipment market in the forecast period mentioned above.

